data.description: Horse Propery!!  2975 square feet custom home with metal roof and finished basement!  Great room has vaulted wood ceilings with wood stove, ceiling fan and built in shelves.  Family room is downstairs with ceiling fan and  wood stove.    Newly remodeled kitchen with granite countertops, new cupboards, and appliances.  New water heater and heat pump with warranty.  Lots of storage with a utility room and bonus room.  Spacious private fenced yard with storage shed. 2 car garage with attached work bench.
